extendedInfo.description: ** No longer supported.  Sorry folks! **** This app does NOT play music! It's a LIST of songs that you enter yourself! **** Please save yourself some trouble and read the description carefully!  This app does NOT play music! :)**My Karaoke List gives karaoke lovers the ability to keep track of all of their favorite songs they like to sing at karaoke by entering them into an easy-to-read list. Make setlists, mark favorites, ban songs, rate your performances, and more. It's simple, fast, easy to use, and built specifically for the karaoke enthusiast.Ever been out somewhere and heard a song you wanted to sing at karaoke?  Use this app to quickly jot it down so you can remember it for your next karaoke night.  Instead of texting, emailing yourself, or writing it down on a napkin, you can now have it in a handy list!You can also get fast and easy web access to the lyrics of any song in your list, as well as one-click access to the YouTube video for singing reference.  This makes it easy to get the lyrics quickly when your karaoke turn is coming up.Features:* Keep a list of your karaoke songs* Keep track of which songs you've sang already* One click access to the lyrics or YouTube video* Mark songs as favorites* Make a setlist for your upcoming karaoke event* Post your setlists to Facebook for your friends to see* Keep track of 'banned' songs * Rate yourself on your singing performancesCheck out the website for more info: http://www.mykaraokelist.coNote: This app does not play music or karaoke tunes.

reviews.title: Good tool for song list.
reviews.comment: I can definitely use this tool.  Suggestions: a field for tracking pitch and possibly free form notes; maybe even a field for the preferred manufacturer code and track number.   A toggle to display song title first, then artist would be helpful.  I like the sort options and the ability to mark favorites.  The stars will be helpful especially when the ability to add manufacturer\'s  codes is available.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Good app
reviews.comment: Like it for keeping track of my karaoke songs...would like to see a place to keep notations ...such as..do I sing a particular song in a certain key or is this song popular in a certain venue ...otherwise it\'s a good app
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Great potential
reviews.comment: This app is quite useful as is. Just being able to track your own karaoke list has a benefit. I can only imagine how many stars this app will garner over time. If you\'re looking to store a list of songs and artists this app looks like a good place to start.
reviews.author: A Google User

I use it not only for my karaoke list but Im a singer and its handy that way as well. Bells id like to see, a way to capture a song like shazam, a way to capture lyrics would be nice. And when you add a song have the cursor in the field. Over all I LOVE IT. Super useful.
